  "original_title": "\u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bc1 ; \u0b9f\u0bb2\u0bb8\u0bcd - \u0b9a\u0b9c\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc1\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0baf\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Presidential election; Dulles - Sajith's presentation",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "4 main candidates are vying for the presidential vacancy created by the resignation of former President Gotabaya Rajapaksa. The candidates who have entered the field have also expressed their opinions about their decision.",
        "Member of Parliament Dalus Alagaperuma and Leader of the Opposition Sajith Premadasa posted this on their Twitter page, announcing that they will contest the presidential election to be held in Parliament next Wednesday.",
        "Member of Parliament Dallas Alagapperuma has said that he has decided to run as a presidential candidate so that the opposition parties can form a consensus government for the first time in history.",
        "At the same time, Leader of the Opposition Sajith Premadasa said that he is trying to make it clear to the opposing party that cooperation with corruption and crony politics will no longer be useful.",
        "'I have decided to run as a presidential candidate with the expectation of forming a unified government for the first time in history with the main opposition party and other opposition parties. Its main objective is to put an end to the culture of corrupt politics that has been seen continuously in history.' mentioned that.",
        "'Extremely difficult programs have been put in place to secure the co-operation of the other party. We are trying to make it clear to them that cooperation with corruption and crony politics will no longer be useful.' posted that."
      ],
